Lynn Merrick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lynn_Merrick 0 Lynn Merrick (November 19, 1919 – March 25, 2007) was an American actress who appeared in over 40 films during the 1940s, mainly for Columbia and Republic Studios.
